node.text:
The Yashiro Commission is responsible for the sacred matters and cultural affairs of Inazuma. The Shirasagi Himegimi handles various official duties with dignified poise.
However, when the Heron returns home, she is back to being simply Ayaka, a girl whose true desire remains hidden within her heart.
But this time, I'm in your company, Traveler. My wish may soon come true.
#GenshinImpact #Ayaka #teaser

node.title: Character Teaser - "Kamisato Ayaka: The Homeward Heron" | Genshin Impact

node.text:
A foreign thunderstorm tears the sky apart, splitting eternity. Flashes of lightning cut through the darkness, as a god's will manifests.
Overcome endless thunderstorms, set foot on the island of cherry blossoms, and witness the Eternity pursued by Her Excellency, the Almighty Narukami Ogosho.
#GenshinImpact #2.0 #preview

node.title: Version 2.0 "The Immovable God and the Eternal Euthymia" Trailer | Genshin

"There will always be those who dare to brave the lightning's glow."
Before stepping into the endless storm, the wandering samurai reminisces about bygone times...
#GenshinImpact #kazuha #teaser

node.text:
The clouds float above the vast mountains, the sky is azure and the water is still. It's a beautiful day to create poetry.
It's a pity that there are always people who don't appreciate the beauty of literature...
But it matters naught. When the wind of the sword settles, the fallen leaves will drift through the wind and the poems will come to life again.
#GenshinImpact #kazuha #character #demo

node.title: New Character Demo - "Kaedehara Kazuha: Wandering Winds" | Genshin Impact

node.text:
The journey following his escape from Inazuma will be long and fraught with peril, something Kaedehara Kazuha is well aware of.
The moon floats in the sky, and a gentle breeze blows by. Though a storm is coming, the ronin shall brave it with song and wine.
#GenshinImpact #kazuha #character #teaser

node.title: Character Teaser - "Kaedehara Kazuha: Moonlit Breeze" | Genshin Impact

node.text:
The ideal summer day should have a refreshing sea breeze, radiant sunshine, and a riveting melody drifting through the wind.
And... golden sands where one can link fingers, hum tunes, and skip through the waves with someone special.
#GenshinImpact #summer #beach

node.text:
With the dance of a sinner, a rebellious heir shatters the shackles of glacial ice.
Under the curtain of the dark night, the flickering candlelight illuminates the sharp edge of a cold blade.

#GenshinImpact #character #Eula

node.text:
Should you be willing to share a table with a less-than-sober Eula, drinking alone in a Mondstadt tavern deep into the night, you might hear her stories about the many "scores" she'll have to settle due to the day's events.
But... is she really going to take revenge for these things?

#GenshinImpact #Eula #Character

node.text:
Between drama and history, fact fades into fiction, yet the truth remains.
Between mountains and mankind, the transient is subsumed, the everlasting endures.
Between friends, a thousand ages ago is but yesterday.
#GenshinImpact #storyteaser

node.title: Story Teaser: Through the Eyes of a Dragon

#GenshinImpact #characterdemo #Yanfei

The City of Freedom is old in years but young at heart, innocent in spirit despite a history mired in complexity.

#GenshinImpact #Rosaria

node.text:
Although Ayaka has long since mastered the Kamisato Art Tachi Jutsu, she continues to persevere in her practice.
However, the servants have noticed that she is training much more than usual lately...
#GenshinImpact #ayaka #character #demo

node.text:
Happy birthday Tartaglia!
#GenshinImpact #tartaglia #childe #happybirthday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Genshin Impact on July 20, 2021. May be an anime-style image.

node.text:
Happy Birthday, Tartaglia.
Haha, what a great sparring session! I didn't expect your martial arts to have improved so much.
This makes me more excited about our future duels!
I feel hungry after such a good fight. You?
If you don't have any other plans, how about coming to try my cooking today?
#GenshinImpact #tartaglia #childe #happybirthday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Genshin Impact on July 14, 2021. May be a cartoon.

node.text:
Happy Birthday, Hu Tao!

"Paimon, you have to catch all four people if you wanna win!"
"Eh? But if we count you, Paimon, and the Traveler, there's only three of us, right?"
"That's not entirely true..."
"...Don't say such scary things!"
#GenshinImpact #hutao #happybirthday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Genshin Impact on July 14, 2021. May be an anime-style image.

node.text:
Today is Hu Tao's birthday!

Oh! What a coincidence to meet you here today—
Hmm, you mean this isn't a chance encounter? Haha, did you come to Wuwang Hill to look for me specially?
Looks like you've heard the good news. It's my birthday today!
Perfect, let's go to Wanmin Restaurant and have a feast together!
Thanks to hou for her art~
#GenshinImpact #hutao #happybirthday

node.text:
Ayaka, known by all as the Princess, takes care of the clan's internal and external affairs. She is a figure greatly admired by the people for her beauty, dignified demeanor, and noble character.
#GenshinImpact #ayaka

node.text:
The Yashiro Commission is responsible for the sacred matters and cultural affairs of Inazuma. The Shirasagi Himegimi handles various official duties with dignified poise.
However, when the Heron returns home, she is back to being simply Ayaka, a girl whose true desire remains hidden within her heart.
But this time, I'm in your company, Traveler. My wish may soon come true.
#GenshinImpact #Ayaka #teaser

node.text:
A foreign thunderstorm tears the sky apart, splitting eternity. Flashes of lightning cut through the darkness, as a god's will manifests.
Overcome endless thunderstorms, set foot on the island of cherry blossoms, and witness the Eternity pursued by Her Excellency, the Almighty Narukami Ogosho.
#GenshinImpact #2.0 #preview

node.text:
Dear Travelers,
The Genshin Impact Preview will premiere on the official Twitch channel at 8:00 AM (UTC-4) on July 9th >>> https://www.twitch.tv/genshinimpactofficial
The official YouTube channel will release the recording on July 9 at 12:00 PM (UTC-4) >>> https://www.youtube.com/c/GenshinImpact
During the program, Dawei(Co-Founder of miHoYo) and the Dev team will share their insight on the anticipated content in the new version.Look out for the redemption code drop in the livestream. Follow us now to get the most up to date information! See you all there, Travelers!
#GenshinImpact #preview #newversion

node.text:
Happy Birthday, Barbara!
I asked you to come to this place because I want to present a special performance for you.
You have always supported me and been there for me. I haven't forgotten any of it, and I want to convey all my thanks through this song!
It's my first time singing it, I'm a little nervous...
Ahem...
One, two...
—Let the show begin~☆
